Changelog:

This is the first release for LXDE Desktop environment.

Added Japanese edition which differs only in boot parameters.

Updated to the up-to-date official base as of 2023-02-03.

Changed a look of desktop wallpaper from the default.


--- NOTE (Known bugs) ---

Each MX Tool should start from command line, as it might NOT start up from Main Menu.
To fix it, please install LXDE PolicyKit as below:

 apt install lxpolkit

Audio is muted by default (this is not a bug).

End.

